Let's Stay in Touch
PORKY'S BAYSIDE
Hungry Yet? Stop on by!
Here at Porky’s Bayside BBQ, we welcome questions, feedback, and suggestions. Without you, there is no us—which just goes to show how much we appreciate you being here! Whether you’re joining us for a hearty breakfast, savory BBQ, fresh seafood, flavorful lobster, or hand-crafted sushi, we’re proud to serve it all with a side of island hospitality. Relax with our famous mojitos, take in the views at our open-air waterfront restaurant and Tiki bar, and enjoy nightly live music that sets the perfect tone for your Keys experience.
Located in the heart of the Florida Keys, we happily welcome guests from Marathon, Islamorada, Key Largo, Key West, and Big Pine Key. Drop us a line—we’d love to hear your thoughts and continue making your time with us unforgettable!

A Local Favorite – Good Eats & Drinks at Our Tiki Bar in Marathon FL
Who We Are
Our full-service restaurant offers breakfast, lunch, dinner, and a sushi menu that is bound to have something for everyone. Relax at our lively Tiki Bar in Marathon FL and enjoy tropical cocktails with a view. Seize the day and take advantage of our in-house water sport amenities, including jet skis, snorkeling, sunset tours, sand bar trips, and exciting charter fishing trips!
Best Restaurant in Florida
Known for our good food and friendly island atmosphere. Our unique location has hosted famous Keys visitors and celebrities since the 1950s, including such notables as Ernest Hemmingway, Jimmy Hoffa, and Elizabeth Taylor. Originally known as “Bill Thompson’s Villas and Marina”, it was the place to be. We know that it still is!
